text: Jeepney phaseout? No. Ang dapat i-phaseout ay yung mga lintik na PUV driver na barubal sa kalsada. Mga jeepney drives, bus drivers, UV Express drivers at taxi drivers na siraulo ang dapat tanggalin. Ewan ko ba kung bakit ang dali-dali kumuha ng driver’s license sa Pinas.

“‘Many are now eager to leave the cooperatives. They’ve had enough of the abuses and fake leaders,’ Elmer Forro of No to PUV Phaseout Coalition said.

Still, he called for an official memorandum from DOTr to make Dizon’s assurance legally binding.”
